33 school service under subdivision (4A) of this section or paragraph (p) of subdivision (1) of
34 section 4. The creditable service allowable under this subdivision for any member shall not
35 exceed 4 years. Members in service of a retirement system who make application for this
36 creditable service shall be notified by the retirement board of their eligibility for this creditable
37 service, and, if they are eligible, shall also be notified by the retirement board that they have the
38 following options: (1) to purchase the service in a lump sum within 180 days after the notice, or
39 (2) to enter into an installment agreement within 180 days after the notice to pay for the
40 creditable service.
